angstd.ui.views.domainview.manager
Class DomainViewManagerFactory

java.lang.Object
  angstd.ui.views.domainview.manager.DomainViewManagerFactory

public class DomainViewManagerFactory
extends java.lang.Object

A class creating all needed DomainViewManagerFactory.DomainViewManager which are needed to provide the complete manager driven functionality for a DomainView.

When initializing the view, it will iterate over all enumeration entries defined in this factory and creates an instance to it.
Therefore to add additional manager to the DomainView you just need to make two entries in this factory and add the getMethod to the DomainView.

Andreas Held
